text: Thomas Cross (1887 - 1963) was a British diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1963 deaths Category:British male divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
